---
import SectionHeader from "@/components/SectionHeader.astro";
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="About"
  metaDesc="About Nick Taylor - Microsoft MVP, GitHub Star, Software Developer, and Developer Advocate."
  socialImage="/assets/images/page-og/about.jpg"
  pageType="Page"
>
  <article class="space-y-12">
    <header>
      <SectionHeader title="About" headingLevel={1} />

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
        <img
          class="w-48 h-48 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-xl object-cover"
          src="/assets/images/colour-headshot-500x500.jpg"
          alt="Headshot of Nick Taylor"
          loading="lazy"
        />

        <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
          <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
            Hi! My name is <strong>Nick Taylor (<a href="/socials">@nickytonline</a>)</strong
            >. I am a Microsoft MVP, GitHub Star, Software Developer, and
            Developer Advocate based in <strong>Montreal, Quebec, Canada</strong>.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            I've been building software for over twenty years and contributing
            to open source for about half that. I've worked at <a
              href="https://opensauced.pizza"
              class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
              >OpenSauced</a
            >, <a
              href="https://dev.to"
              class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
              >dev.to</a
            >, and <a
              href="https://www.netlify.com/"
              class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
              >Netlify</a
            >, and now I'm in developer relations at <a
              href="https://pomerium.com"
              class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
              >Pomerium</a
            >.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            You can browse <a
              href="/projects"
              class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
              >my open-source projects</a
            >, and check out the full list on <a
              href="https://github.com/nickytonline"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
              >GitHub</a
            >.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
            You'll often find me live streaming tech content, either solo or
            with friends from the community. I also run the
            <a
              href="https://onetipaweek.com"
              class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
              >One Tip a Week</a
            > newsletter and mentor in the
            <a
              href="https://discord.gg/PcNdE2jJ"
              class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
              >Let's Get Technical</a
            > community.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <SectionHeader title="Speaking & Conferences" headingLevel={2} />
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        I speak at conferences like <strong>All Things Open</strong>, <strong>ConFoo</strong>, <strong>BlackHat USA</strong>,
        <strong>AI Engineer Europe</strong>, <strong>SREday</strong>, and <strong>MCP Dev Summit</strong>. I usually talk about web dev, open source,
        AI agents, or Zero Trust security.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        You can browse <a
          href="/talks"
          class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
          >all my talks and presentations</a
        > for slide decks, recordings, and more.
      </p>
      <div class="pt-2">
        <a
          href="mailto:nick@nickyt.co?subject=Speaking%20Inquiry"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-pink-600 text-white font-semibold text-base hover:bg-pink-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-pink-600 focus:ring-offset-2 dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-900 transition-colors"
        >
          Book me to speak
          <span class="text-xl">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <SectionHeader title="Content Creation" headingLevel={2} />
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        I <a
          href="https://twitch.tv/nickytonline"
          class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
          >stream on Twitch</a>
        and
        <a
          href="https://youtube.com/@nickytonline"
          class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
          >YouTube</a>,
        write about whatever I'm figuring out, and send out
        <a
          href="https://onetipaweek.com"
          class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
          >One Tip a Week</a>
        — a short newsletter with practical dev tips.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <SectionHeader title="Connect" headingLevel={2} />
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        Wanna get in touch? Drop me an e-mail at <span
          class="font-semibold text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400"
          >nick at nickyt dot co</span
        >. You can also find me <a
          href="/socials"
          class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-semibold hover:underline focus:underline focus:outline-none"
          >across the web</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>

  <p class="text-center text-muted-foreground mt-4">
    Open graph image by
    <a
      href="https://unsplash.com/@iamfelicia?utm_source=unsplash&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=creditCopyText"
    >
      Felicia Buitenwerf
    </a>
    on
    <a
      href="https://unsplash.com/photos/this-is-who-i-am-5yn5rGI5IUw?utm_source=unsplash&utm_medium=referral&utm_content=creditCopyText"
    >
      Unsplash
    </a>
  </p>
</MainLayout>
